				\begin{document}$$W_{{{\text{ad}}}} = (E_\text{slab1}^{{}} + E_\text{slab2} - E_{{\text{int}}}^{{}} )/A{,}$$\end{document}where Eslab1 and Eslab1 are the total energies of slab1 and slab2, Eint is the total energy of the interface system including slab1 and slab2, and A is the interface area.
